rows.label: tev001394_MSG0001
rows.name:
What a surprise to cross paths with you here,
[ST:playername ]. I hope you are doing well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_JNK0010
rows.name: Wonder about Rock

rows.label: tev001394_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Celica where Rock is.

rows.label: tev001394_JNK0020
rows.name: Wonder about Cat

rows.label: tev001394_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Celica if she has been petting the cat.

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0002
rows.name:
Rock is at work, doing his part for this fair city.
So I am by myself for the moment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0003
rows.name:
I was just exploring the commercial district when I
happened across this cat and decided to follow it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0004
rows.name: That led me to here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0005
rows.name: I most certainly have![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0006
rows.name:
I was just exploring the commercial district when I
happened across this cat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0007
rows.name: It was so cute, I couldn't help but follow it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0008
rows.name: That led me to here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0009
rows.name: The craftsmanship on this cat is truly exceptional.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0010
rows.name:
I couldn't believe it when Lin told me that it was
artificial.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0011
rows.name:
It appears completely real to the eye as well as touch.
And it's just as moody and mischievous as a live cat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_JNK0030
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev001394_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask if there were cats on Celica's world.

rows.label: tev001394_JNK0040
rows.name: Brag

rows.label: tev001394_SEL0041
rows.name: Boast that the cat is an exemplar of human ingenuity.

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0012
rows.name:
Yes. Just as we look slightly different from humans,
so did our cats differ slightly from yours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0013
rows.name: It is certainly a stunning and mysterious coincidence.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0014
rows.name: Our worlds were so far apart, as you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0015
rows.name:
At yet, they were home to two species as similar as
yours and mine, as well as two cute catlike species.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0016
rows.name: I suppose you're right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0017
rows.name:
How interesting that humans use their technological
prowess to re-create the sensations of their homeworld.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0018
rows.name:
Yet I imagine the Ganglion use theirs to create nothing
but weapons of war.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001394_MSG0019
rows.name:
Perhaps this depth of spirit is the reason humanity has
managed to retain its sense of humor and accept so
many xenoforms so readily.[ST:wait ]
